{"tid":2085483,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"[HKUSPACE]召集所有太空人面孔(50) 完sem了！","createTime":"2020-06-30T01:57:47.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-08T08:05:10.000Z","uid":201445,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":39,"replies":[{"pid":"ad3d1b0de2aa3e6dcb97ede8cabe5cdf0a713a2e","tid":2085483,"uid":201445,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T01:57:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/24/141044_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F24%2F141044_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png&h=300dcdc9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n歡迎各位fm bb，有咩關於space嘅問題可以喺道問<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nyear 2同老鬼都可以幫手答<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong>Frequently Asked Questions:&amp;nbsp;</strong><br />\n<br />\n1.點DEFER學費?&amp;nbsp;<br />\n打封英文解釋信&amp;nbsp;<br />\n加埋offer letter+經濟困難證明文件+留位費收據既copy&amp;nbsp;<br />\n交份copy去space院校就得&amp;nbsp;<br />\n帶埋所有文件正本比人check&amp;nbsp;<br />\n之後返去等通知&amp;nbsp;<br />\n詳情可以打去space問&amp;nbsp;<br />\nby梵高的星夜&amp;nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n2.咩係天書?&amp;nbsp;<br />\n係KEC十樓，有每年不同科升大學的數據，包括公開試成績，GPA，IELTS，interview問題&amp;nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n3. SPACE最伏係邊幾科?&amp;nbsp;<br />\n沒有廢科，只有廢人&amp;nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n4. 常用連結<br />\n<a href=\"https://learner.hkuspace.hku.hk/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Flearner.hkuspace.hku.hk%2F&d=BZN1wbl1lFElyj%2BXlEN3CD11NNBcSSu27FcfjCvRQ4I%3D&h=c9883d6a\" target=\"_blank\">https://learner.hkuspace.hku.hk/</a><br />\n<br />\n交學費、add drop swap科、睇timetable、apply locker、download notes、交功課、reference letter、圖書館book 房、睇/買transcript、<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\"> withdraw from study</span>全部經portal入到<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">港大附屬學院成績驕人 是你首選</span></strong></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/24/141911_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F24%2F141911_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=976e9c84&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">1/3升讀<del>三</del>兩大 <br />\n2/3升讀八大UGC</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/24/142846_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F24%2F142846_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=13bc46e8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n同學連SEM BREAK都不忘回校，手執書卷努力溫習，反映學術氣氛濃厚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong>關於killer......</strong><br />\n唔少人都話space有killer，永遠榮譽太空人港英狗（戇鳩仔）咁講：<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/24/145356_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F24%2F145356_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=f865cd3e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n不過我自己咁睇，我覺得好多因素影響grade嘅，每個lecturer點都要派啲A+派啲B-，如果你嗰班多勁人，有對比之下你自然睇落差啲；相反你嗰班本身廢廢哋，而你水平又稍為高啲啲，assignment同present做得好啲，個A/A+自然袋袋平安。加埋出grade前每個lecturer比嘅grade都會微調，assignment A+final grade拉落A A-拉上A+都有，9分努力1分運氣，做好自己結果唔會太差嘅，唔對路咪add drop轉班囉。<br />\n<br />\n唔好聽到人話某個lecturer教得好就狗衝（尤其中英文），入到去比成班英文啪啪聲嘅學霸堂堂屌打，出gdp嘅時候就欲哭無淚。某啲傳說中嘅killer無人reg，結果一個學霸都無，呢個就係你大顯身手嘅時候，多啲答問題問問題唔好怕醜，啲廢人一定笑鳩你多嘢講，你要記住平時分就係咁樣來，出gdp嗰陣你揸隻A佢揸隻B，睇下邊個笑到最後。同埋千祈唔好遲到同埋走堂，平時分執豆咁執，蘇州過後無艇搭，無咗呢10%話知你全部assignment A+ final grade都唔會上到A+。機會只係劉備勤力嘅人，做人做狗自己決定<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">*雖然最頂寫住「沒有廢科，只有廢人」，只係祖訓來架咋，EE(energy &amp; environment)、AA(Art appreciation)、IPhil(Introduction to philosophy)呢三科係大伏，揀咗嘅自己睇路，drop科保平安 </span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">*To AS/AAS/AP既同學們，切勿做學校Placement，功課多、工時長、人工低同要日日帶老母返工，做錯野好易爛grade；要做就自已出去搵，做Project更稱 心</span><br />\n<br />\n祝各位太空人早日返回地球<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">比啲掙扎！</span></strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/24/143351_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F24%2F143351_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=f160a5d6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">I want you to 過三爆四</span></strong>"},{"pid":"b7bb116e4ed6983ad906a57df5b9768abcccf03b","tid":2085483,"uid":235316,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T02:26:50.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">7一維園見</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">Facebook ig airdrop</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9vzHhbe.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9vzHhbe.jpg&h=c0777e33&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/HXtg54z.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHXtg54z.jpg&h=eae3d5c9&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Qizj3Rf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQizj3Rf.jpg&h=d33e105b&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Sg0OXbk.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSg0OXbk.jpg&h=791a8ec6&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ivfSEpG.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FivfSEpG.jpg&h=e07fd1e0&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"964ec41cc334bb20f954dd45c418b3bdbf5531fa","tid":2085483,"uid":225101,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T02:31:34.000Z","msg":"出grade<img src=\"/ass